data.title: The Compatibilities in Zodiacs
data.meta_description: THE COMPATIBILITIES IN ZODIACS - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. The document discusses various zodiac systems from around the world and their relationships and compatibilities. It describes the Chinese zodiac's 12 animals and their association with 5 elements. It also briefly outlines other zodiacs including the Australian, Aztec, Arab, Classical Western, Vedic Indian, and Native American zodiacs. The purpose is to analyze compatibilities between different zodiac signs across cultures.
